Class IdBasedBinding

java.lang.Object
  de.fuberlin.wiwiss.jenaext.sparql.IdBasedBinding

public class IdBasedBinding
extends Object

An identifier based binding is a mapping from query variables that are represented by identifiers to values which are also represented by identifiers.

Author:
Olaf Hartig
